OL,3,CDumfries cafe announces closure 'with
OL,4,Ca heavy heart'
OL,6,FA Dumfries cafe has announced that it
OL,7,Fwill be closing due to financial
OL,8,Fpressures.
OL,10,FThe Frothy Bike Company has announced
OL,11,Fthe closure of its cafe on the
OL,12,FWhitesands in the town.
OL,14,FThe cafe will shut on Sunday, 7 April,
OL,15,Falthough the bike department of the
OL,16,Fbusiness will remain open.
OL,18,FOwner Ross Anderson explains that the
OL,19,Ffinancial pressures the cafe has been
OL,20,Fexperiencing have stemmed from the
OL,21,FCovid pandemic.
