OL,6,FHe said: "We are closing the cafe for
OL,7,Ffinancial reasons. It has never really
OL,8,Fbeen strong since Covid, we kept
OL,9,Ftelling ourselves it would get better
OL,10,Fbut it's not getting better.
OL,12,F"The general consumer isn't what they
OL,13,Fused to be before the pandemic.
OL,15,F"So we have struggled to get the
OL,16,Ffootfall back up, and staff
OL,17,Frecruitment as well, the hospitality
OL,18,Ftrade was hit pretty hard trying to
OL,19,Fbring in good staff. We lost all of
OL,20,Four staff through Covid, everyone went
OL,21,Faway and got other jobs."
