OL,6,FThe cafe has been open for five years
OL,7,Fin .
OL,9,FRoss added: "I am looking forward not
OL,10,Fto having the flood warning texts come
OL,11,Fthrough to me at 1am.
OL,13,F"You are waking up in a sweat trying
OL,14,Fto get the sandbags and the pumps
OL,15,Forganised, I am looking forward to not
OL,16,Fworrying about that."
OL,18,FStephen Montgomery from the Scottish
OL,19,FHospitality Group believes the
OL,20,Fhospitality industry is still
OL,21,Frecovering from the pandemic.
