OL,6,FHe said: "The pandemic really hit the
OL,7,Fhospitality sector, really more than
OL,8,Fany other sector across the economy.
OL,10,F"We had chefs who were home all of the
OL,11,Ftime and decided to go onto other
OL,12,Fjobs. You had other people in the
OL,13,Fsector that went into other jobs in
OL,14,Fplaces like supermarkets.
OL,16,F"Any wage inflation has to be added on
OL,17,Fto the consumer. At a time like now
OL,18,Fwhen we are in a cost of living crisis
OL,19,Fit is really hard for us not to pass
OL,20,Fthat on.
